## 🧠 Quick Reference Cheatsheet

```bash
# ── FULL DOCUMENTATION ───────────────────────────────
man ls                      # manual for ls
man 5 /etc/passwd           # manual for passwd file format
man -k keyword              # same as apropos

# ── QUICK HELP ───────────────────────────────────────
ls --help                   # long help flag
curl -h                     # short help flag (some tools)
nmap -h                     # short help (nmap style)

# ── SEARCH MANUALS ───────────────────────────────────
apropos sudo                # find commands related to sudo
apropos password            # find password-related commands
sudo mandb                  # update man page database

# ── NAVIGATING man PAGES ─────────────────────────────
/keyword    # search inside man page
n           # next match
N           # previous match
q           # quit
Space       # next page
b           # previous page
g           # go to top
G           # go to bottom

# ── ONLINE RESOURCES ─────────────────────────────────
# https://explainshell.com  → visual command breakdown
# https://tldr.sh           → simplified man pages (community)
# https://cheat.sh          → cheatsheets from terminal:
curl cheat.sh/ls            # get ls cheatsheet from terminal
```

